        <h1>「 Chess Design for Blind People 」</h1>
        <div class="T__wrap">
            <img class="T__wrap-bg" src="images/work6/xiangqi.jpg" alt="IMG">

            <div class="layout-1">
                <p><em>Chess for the blind</em>
                    <br>
                    We chose blind chess making. Taking into account the blind is a relatively special group, our design has also carried out some special treatment.<br>
                    When drawing the sketch first we take it easy. The beauty that simplicity sometimes brings is more direct than triviality. And we emphasize the theme of facilitating people with disabilities. Convenience is the most important. Without too much modification, the chessboard uses a simple regular geometric protrusion superimposed on the box. The geometric raised shape is also well recognized and does not require time to remember. Such a blind person touches the chess piece can touch its clear outline to determine what kind of pieces it is. Chess pieces at the bottom of the magnet match with the chessboard.<br>
                    In addition to the rules of the chessboard square arrangement, the placement of chess pieces of the location of the magnet, so long as the chess pieces on the board will be very easy to absorb the place you want to place. Chessboard foldable.<br>
                    Chess box for the convenience of storage. Our chess box is layered and well-utilized. There is a gap in the middle of the chess box that can fold the checkerboard into it. Chess pieces can be placed on both sides of pieces, not space.<br>
                    Finally, because the object of chess is blind people, so both sides of the pieces should be easy to distinguish. We designed a pawn side is rough, easy to identify.<br>
                    Based on this design, we have completed the modeling. And ready to use all acrylic finish.
                </p>
